al game lobbies but I was always able to find some games in the global lobby. Also does the game not offer that much for graphic enthusiasts.But as I said, I do recommend the game. After I got the hang of it I started to enjoy the helping, covering and healing, sharing of ammunition, in short: the teamwork.And despite of that, who is going to stop the horrors of mars, if not YOU(!)?I'm doing my part! What about YOU? You wanna live forever?!"
