76561198027156385,Recommended,265590,13238542,"Posted: 5 December, 2014",all,Blue Eyes White Privileged!,"The Starcraft and Warcraft mods, are currently far better. Balance wise, and more. This has potential, but I don't think they will ever change it. Another note. Even after the fixes, there are certain bugs that still hit a large majority of people. I for instance, can play this game, and every once and a blue moon, all the models actually load in. But generally, I am shooting air. Several people in the gorup I play with, suffer this same issue. This was recently tested again. All of us, more than meet the minimum requirments. This game is just poorly optimized, as of yet. If this game ever fixes these major issues, it may be worth picking up.Update 8/3/2015:  While I haven't had a chance to play through to much of it, it has definitely improved on a lot of little things, which actually make a big difference. Better yet, the game is working, and most of the major compadability issues everyone I knew had for the entirety of the beta, are now fixed. As the game is now, I would definitely recomend it. If you like these types of games, you'll probably like this one.  Admitedly, there are a few things I prefer about the Starcraft and Warcraft maps, such as the recon and marksman class, but, overall, this is a nice new twist, and I've played the other maps to death.If you are worried about an unfinished game, have no worries. Everything felt rather complete, and the single player campaign is really well done, including having special features specifically made for the campaign alone that make the game something of a charm. Such as the tactical combat. An interface that slows down time, and allows you to control your entire squad individually. I was wondering how they were going to handle the lack of fellow players with AI, and they nailed it.Truthfully, some of the people online in the community are a bit sour, but there are also some nice, friendly people, just looking to have fun. Also, probably one of the better games to play with a group of friends."
